result.formatted_address: 3 Chui Yi St, Tai Wo Estate, Hong Kong
result.name: 616牛肉火鍋專門店

reviews.text:
Amazing experience having the beef hotpot nearby!
Very reasonable price ($48/$68 @dish) but surely with small portion, this is so perfect for small group of people whom can try more varies of food, esp. you may find over 20 types of meats.
iPad in placing order and their service is very quick (maybe I have my dinner at 17:xx during weekday).
Waiter is very professional in explaining the menu, ordering process, and the difference of different part of beef!
Very considerate in proving the USB charges for guests to use (similar to Taiwan’s hotpot restaurant).
You may get a good deal in some app for special discount on certain time slot. 😏☺️
Reserved table for 3 at 1930 on Sat. However, waiting for more than 30 mins still doesn’t come up with empty seats. Terrible management!
Nice food.  But not enough a/c
Amazingly simple beef hotpot which tastes fantastic!
Good hotpot. The beef is fresh but in small piece
